    "title": "Reliance Retail is Hiring: Floor Manager (Principal)",
    "description": "Reliance Retail invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Floor Manager at our Patna location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Reliance Retail:\nReliance Retail is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Reliance Retail!",
